{{地區用詞|tw=不活化疫苗<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-tw |url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/5457915/ |title=不活化疫苗inactivated vaccine |date= |publisher=國家教育研究院 雙語詞彙、 學術名詞暨辭書資訊網 |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2021-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204010633/https://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/5457915/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> |cn=灭活疫苗|hk=cn|start={{lang-en| Inactivated vaccine}}|as=稱作|before='''|after='''}}，是指由已杀灭的[[病原体|病原体]]制成之疫苗。制造灭活疫苗过程中，杀灭病原体的方式包括：加热杀灭、利用化学方法（如[[甲醛|甲醛]]）杀灭，以及利用[[放射治療|放射线]]杀灭<ref name="TypesVaccines">{{cite web|title=Types of Vaccines|url=http://www.vaccines.gov/more_info/types/|accessdate=2016-05-16|date=2013-07-23|publisher=U.S. Department of Health and Human Services|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609071759/http://www.vaccines.gov/more_info/types|archivedate=2013-06-09|website=Vaccines.gov}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=中国医学百科全书|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xukZAQAAMAAJ|year=1980|publisher=上海科学技术出版社|page=50|access-date=2020-11-29|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210072541/https://books.google.com/books?id=xukZAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一部分灭毒疫苗中杀灭的病原体依然以完整形态存在，也有的灭活疫苗会将病原体裂解，亦存在将病原体中的抗原单独提纯出来的灭毒疫苗<ref name="WHOinfluenza">{{cite web|title=Influenza|url=https://www.who.int/biologicals/vaccines/influenza/en/|accessdate=2016-05-16|date=2016-01-07|last=[[世界卫生组织|WHO]] Expert Committee on Biological Standardization|publisher=World Health Organization (WHO)|archive-date=2013-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617180153/https://www.who.int/biologicals/vaccines/influenza/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

灭毒疫苗主要通过其中的抗原诱导[[细胞免疫|细胞免疫]]的产生，一般来说死亡的病原体复杂，抗原成分加工程度较低，故需要多次接种且免疫效果持续较短，但好处是保存与制作容易<ref name="陈芳梅2017">{{cite book|author=陈芳梅|title=微生物学与免疫学基础|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=78zsDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT127|year=2017|publisher=河南科学技术出版社|isbn=978-7-5349-8831-8|page=127}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-55251508 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-09-05 |archive-date=2021-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621090605/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-55251508 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

